dataset_id: SAFARI 2000 SeaWiFS Images for the Southern African Region, 1999-2001
title: SAFARI 2000 SeaWiFS Images for the Southern African Region, 1999-2001
summary: This data set contains Sea-viewing Wide Field-of-view Sensor (SeaWiFS) imagery for the southern African region. These images are Level-1a swaths of the southern African region selected from global area coverage (GAC) at 4.5-km resolution. The data are provided in HDF format files.
